import React, { Component } from 'react'; import '../App.css'; import { Table } from 'reactstrap'; class CycleA extends Component { render() { let load = (this.props.weight-this.props.bar); return (
    1 40% 5x {Math.round(load*4/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*4/10).toFixed(1)}
    2 50% 5x {Math.round(load*5/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*5/10).toFixed(1)}
    3 60% 3x {Math.round(load*6/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*6/10).toFixed(1)}
    40% Warmup Set 1 x 5x : {Math.round(load*4/10).toFixed(1)}kg
    50% Warmup Set 2 x 5x : {Math.round(load*5/10).toFixed(1)}kg
    60% Warmup Set 3 x 3x : {Math.round(load*6/10).toFixed(1)}kg
    65% Working Set 1 5x {Math.round(load*65/100).toFixed(1)}kg
    75% Working Set 2 5x {Math.round(load*75/100).toFixed(1)}kg
    85% Working Set 3 5x+ {Math.round(load*85/100).toFixed(1)}kg
) } } export default CycleA;
